text: Cagles Crossing Multi-Purpose Building Cagles Crossing is an unincorporated community located in Coahoma County, Mississippi, United States. Cagles Crossing is located on Dog Walk Road, approximately north of Rome and approximately south of Dublin. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Coahoma County, Mississippi Category:Unincorporated communities in Mississippi
